In all, 125 hospitals and 4,652,355 records in the four cities were surveyed. From these records, 471 ADEM cases were found in the study population. Among these 471 cases, 59 cases were ruled out owing to residence outside of the geographical areas of study. A total of 412 cases were involved in the incidence calculation. The incidence was 0.32 cases per 100,000 person-years. 